ETA Asia-Pacific |accessdate=2011-08-04 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130209004348/http://www.petaasiapacific.com/feature-world_vegetarian_sexy.asp |archivedate=9 February 2013 |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n* 2012 \u2013 Voted \"India's Greatest Actor\" in [[NDTV]] poll.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://movies.ndtv.com/movie_story.aspx?ID=ENTEN20120213602&subcatg=MOVIESINDIA&keyword=bollywood&nid=260108 |title=NDTV poll: India's greatest actor is... |publisher=ndtv.com |date=2012-08-28 |accessdate=2012-08-28 }}{{dead link|date=September 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n* 2012 \u2013 Voted \"Most-Admired Bollywood Actor\" in a new mobile survey.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/amitabh-bachchan-sridevi-voted-mostadmired-bollywood-actors/1048607/ |title=Amitabh Bachchan, Sridevi voted most-admired Bollywood actors |publisher=indianexpress.com |date=2012-12-21 |accessdate=2012-12-21}}</ref>\n* 2012 \u2013 Voted the \"Hottest Male Vegetarian\" for the fourth time by 'People for the Ethical Treatment of Animals' (PETA).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Tabloid/Amitabh-Bachchan-Vidya-Balan-named-hottest-vegetarians/Article1-984421.aspx |title=Amitabh Bachchan, Vidya Balan named hottest vegetarians |publisher=hindustantimes.com |date=2013-01-03 |accessdate=2013-01-25 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130104141844/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Tabloid/Amitabh-Bachchan-Vidya-Balan-named-hottest-vegetarians/Article1-984421.aspx |archivedate=4 January 2013 }}</ref>\n* 2013 \u2013 Voted the \"Greatest Bollywood Star\" in a UK poll celebrating 100 years of Indian cinema.<ref>{{cite news|url= http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-07-27/news-interviews/40832397_1_amitabh-bachchan-raj-kapoor-rajesh-khanna |title= Amitabh Bachchan crowned greatest Bollywood star |publisher= timesofindia.indiatimes.com |date=2013-07-27 |accessdate=2013-09-11}}</ref>\n* 2019 - Topped India Most Trusted Personality by TRA Research.\n* 2020- Topped India Most Trusted Personality by TRA Research.\n<ref><link rel=\"amphtml\" href=\"https://www.indiantelevision.com/mam/marketing/mam/big-b-is-india-s-most-trusted-personality-tra-research-190520?amp\" /></ref><ref><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://retropoplifestyle.com/old-is-gold-says-tras-most-desired-personality-list-2020/\" /></ref><ref><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://www.mediainfoline.com/tag/tras-most-desired-personality\" /></ref><ref><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://cornerpapes.com/2019/05/21/rajinikanth-is-south-indias-most-trusted-personality-2019-tra-research/\" /></ref>\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of accolades received by Piku]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bachchan, Amitabh}}\n[[Category:Lists of awards received by actor]]\n[[Category:Bollywood lists of awards and nominations]]\n[[Category:Amitabh Bachchan|Awards]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2013}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=March 2013}}\n{{Expand list|date=March 2018}}\n\n{| class=\"infobox\" style=\"width:22em; text-align:left; font-size:90%; vertical-align:middle; background:#eef;\"\n|+ <span style=\"font-size: 10pt\">'''List of awards received by [[Amitabh Bachchan]]'''</span>\n|- style=\"background:white;\"\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[File:The Chief Guest Superstar Amitabh Bachchan addressing at the inauguration of the 45th International Film Festival of India (IFFI-2014), in Panaji, Goa on November 20, 2014.jpg|235px]]<br />{{Small|Bachchan at the 45th International Film Festival of India (IFFI-2014) in [[Panaji]], [[Goa]], [[India]]}}\n|-\n| colspan=\"3\" |\n{| class=\"collapsible collapsed\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n! colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d9e8ff; text-align:center;\"| Awards and nominations\n|- style=\"background:#d9e8ff; text-align:center;\"\n!style=\"vertical-align: middle;\"| Award\n| style=\"background:#cec; font-size: