.com/bollywood/big-star-entertainment-awards-2015-salman-deepika-are-big-winners-1254786</ref>\n|}\n\n==People's Choice Awards==\n{{Main|People's Choice Awards India}}\n'''Winner'''\n* 2012 \u2013 Best Non-Fiction Show Host for ''Kaun Banega Crorepati''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nriheadlines.com/2012/10/peoples-choice-award-winners-salman-priyanka-amitabh/ |title=Peoples choice award winners: Salman, Priyanka & Amitabh |publisher=nriheadlines.com |date=2012-10-28 |accessdate=2012-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022004901/http://www.nriheadlines.com/2012/10/peoples-choice-award-winners-salman-priyanka-amitabh/ |archive-date=22 October 2013 |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n\n==Indian Television Academy Awards==\n{{Main|Indian Television Academy Awards}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year || Category || Show || Result\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2001 || Best Host ||rowspan=\"2\"| ''[[Kaun Banega Crorepati|Kaun Banega Crorepati (Season 1)]]''<ref name=\"ITA-2001\">[http://www.indiantelevisionacademy.com/site/awards_hhita_details_new.php?year=2005 Winners:Indian Television Academy Awards, 2005] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120504215552/http://www.indiantelevisionacademy.com/site/awards_hhita_details_new.php?year=2005 |date=4 May 2012 }}</ref> || rowspan=\"9\" {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Anchor of a Game Show<ref name=\"ITA-2001\"/>\n|-\n| 2005 ||rowspan=\"2\"| Best Anchor of a Game Show ||rowspan=\"2\"| ''[[Kaun Banega Crorepati|Kaun Banega Crorepati (Season 2)]]''<ref name=\"ITA-2001\"/>\n|-\n| 2006<ref>[http://www.indiantelevisionacademy.com/site/awards_hhita_details_new.php?year=2006 Winners:Indian Television Academy Awards, 2006] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210174024/http://www.indiantelevisionacademy.com/site/awards_hhita_details_new.php?year=2006 |date=10 February 2012 }}</ref>\n|-\n| 2007 || The ITA Laurel For 'ULTIMATE EMINENCE'''<ref>[http://www.indiantelevisionacademy.com/site/awards_hhita_detail