7.co.uk/bizasia/indian-telly-awards-2012-winners |archivedate=28 October 2012 |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Indian Television Awards==\n'''Winner'''\n* 2000 \u2013 Screen Videocon Awards: Best Anchor Award for ''Kaun Banega Crorepati''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tribuneindia.com/2001/20010122/nation.htm#5 |title=The Tribune, Chandigarh, India \u2013 Nation |publisher=Tribuneindia.com |date= |accessdate=2011-08-04}}</ref>\n\n==BIG Television Awards==\n{{Main|BIG Television Awards}}\n'''Winner'''\n* 2011 \u2013 Shaksiyat of the year for ''Kaun Banega Crorepati''\n* 2011 \u2013 \"Distinguished Personality\" .<ref>{{cite web|url=http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/articles/story90063.htm |title=Amitabh wins 'distinguished personality' award |publisher=Zeenews.india.com |date= |accessdate=2011-08-04}}</ref>\n\n==Other awards==\n'''Winner'''\n* 1970 \u2013 National Award for Best Newcomer for ''[[Saat Hindustani]]''<ref name=\"in.rediff.com\">http://in.rediff.com/movies/2007/aug/09amitabh.htm</ref><ref name=\"photogallery.indiatimes.com\">{{cite news |title=Happy b'day Big B |url=http://photogallery.indiatimes.com/celebs/indian-stars/Happy-bday-Big-B/articleshow/16757174.cms | work=The Times Of India}}</ref><ref name=\"koimoi.com\">http://www.koimoi.com/actor/amitabh-bachchan/</ref><ref name=\"dnaindia.com\">http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report_amitabh-bachchan-d-ramanaidu-receive-national-film-awards_1456683</ref>\n* 1970 \u2013 \"Saraswati Award\" for ''[[Anand (1970 film)|Anand]]''<ref>http://www.ishopindian.com/shop/product.php?printable=Y&productid=22174&cat=0&page=7</ref>\n* 1989 \u2013 Lifetime Achievement Award from the [[Rotary Club]] of Bombay (Mumbai).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.screenindia.com/archive/archive_fullstory.php?content_id=8343 |title=Screen > The Business of Entertainment |publisher=Screenindia.com |date=2004-06-11 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071102174739/http://www.screenindia