on]]||[[Sion Airport]]||||\n|-\n}\n\n==Fleet   ==\nAs of April 2020, the flyBAIR fleet comprised of the following aircraft:<ref name=\"fleetofficial\">[https://www.flybair.ch/Fliegen/Embraer-E190-E1 flybair.ch - \"Embraer E190-E1\"] (German) retrieved 23 April 2020 </ref>\n\n<center>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; text-align:center\"\n|+ flyBAIR fleet\n|- \n!Aircraft\n!In service\n!Orders\n!Passengers<ref name=\"fleetofficial\"/>\n!Notes\n|- \n|[[Embraer E-Jet family#E-190 and 195|Embraer 190]]\n|&mdash;\n|1\n|112<ref name=\"fleetofficial\"/>\n|\n|-\n!Total\n!&mdash;\n!1\n!colspan=\"2\"|\n|}\n</center>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category-inline|flyBAIR|flyBAIR}}\n* [http://flybair.ch Official website]\n\n{{Portal bar|Switzerland|Companies|Aviation}}\n{{Airlines of Switzerland}}\n\n[[Category:Airlines established in 2020]]\n[[Category:2020 establishments in Switzerland]]\n[[Category:Companies based in Bern]]\n", "name_user": "TrainNutter", "label": "safe", "comment": "Fixed placement of destinations table", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/FlyBAIR"}
